## Changeset Lifecycle

### 1. Created (`@plan-ft-dev`)

**State**: New changeset document created
**Status**: `🚧 In Progress`
**Scope**: All items `[ ]` (unchecked)

**Actions**:
- Document created with full template
- Affected packages listed
- State A, State B, Delta defined
- Implementation milestones planned
- Acceptance tests defined

### 2. In Progress

**State**: Active development
**Status**: `🚧 In Progress`
**Scope**: Items progress from `[ ]` → `[~]` → `[x]`

**Actions**:
- Implementation milestones checked off as completed
- Acceptance tests checked off as they pass
- Scope checkboxes updated by various rules/commands
- Technical debt items added as discovered
- Decisions documented as made
- **Refactoring issues tracked** as discovered by validation rules
- **Validation results** added after each validation run

**Updated by**:
- `/update-context-docs` - Updates Scope, milestones
- `@ft-dev` - Creates acceptance tests, updates Scope, adds refactoring issues
- `@red` - Adds refactoring issues from TDD red phase
- `@test-acceptance` - Checks off passing tests, updates Scope
- `/validate-changes` - Adds validation results and refactoring issues
- `/validate-tests` - Adds test validation results and refactoring issues
- `/validate-prod-ready` - Validates technical debt resolution, updates Scope, adds validation results
- `/analyze-clean-code` - Adds code quality validation results and refactoring issues
- `refactor` (subagent) - Checks off completed refactorings, adds results

### 3. Complete

**State**: All work finished
**Status**: `✅ Complete`
**Scope**: All items `[x]` (checked)

**Prerequisites**:
- All Scope checkboxes marked `[x]`
- All implementation milestones checked off
- All acceptance tests passing
- Technical debt addressed or documented
- Code quality validated
- **All validation results** show passing status
- **All refactoring issues** addressed or documented

**Actions**:
- Status changed to `✅ Complete`
- Ready for wrapping

### 4. Wrapped (`/wrap-context-docs`)

**State**: Applied to dev docs, deleted
**Status**: Deleted

**Actions**:
- Changeset applied to package READMEs and `packages/{pkg}/docs/`
- State B content merged into stable docs
- Delta, milestones, Scope sections removed from final docs
- **Refactoring Needed** section removed (issues should be resolved)
- **Validation Results** section removed (not preserved)
- Changeset **deleted**: `YYYY-MM-DD-changeset-name.md` (not archived)
- Release note-style summary added to `packages/{pkg}/docs/changesets.md`

